      "text": "Ad Revenue vs. Creator Rewards"
    },
    {
      "id": "t30",
      "tag": "strong",
      "text": "YouTube AdSense"
    },
    {
      "id": "t31",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "pays per video via a direct CPM model — creators keep 55% of ad revenue from their specific content. High-niche content earns $15–$40+ RPM."
    },
    {
      "id": "t32",
      "tag": "strong",
      "text": "TikTok Creator Rewards"
    },
    {
      "id": "t33",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "pays from a shared pool based on platform-wide engagement. Maximum effective RPM rarely exceeds $0.08 per 1,000 views."
    },
    {
      "id": "t34",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "YouTube pays 75–150× more per view in direct platform revenue than TikTok. But TikTok gets you to brand deals faster."
    },
