    {
      "id": "t64",
      "tag": "button",
      "text": "Does TikTok or YouTube pay more overall?"
    },
    {
      "id": "t65",
      "tag": "div",
      "text": "YouTube pays dramatically more per view through AdSense. However, TikTok's faster growth mechanics can accelerate a creator's path to brand deals that match or exceed YouTube's total income."
    },
    {
      "id": "t66",
      "tag": "button",
      "text": "Can you cross-post TikTok content to YouTube Shorts?"
    },
    {
      "id": "t67",
      "tag": "div",
      "text": "Yes — many creators repurpose TikTok videos as YouTube Shorts. Note that YouTube's algorithm may deprioritize content with visible TikTok watermarks."
    },
    {
      "id": "t68",
      "tag": "button",
      "text": "Is it better to start on TikTok or YouTube in 2026?"
    },
    {
      "id": "t69",
      "tag": "div",
      "text": "TikTok is generally faster for audience building. YouTube is better for compounding long-term income. Most successful creators today start on TikTok to grow an audience, then invest in YouTube for monetization depth."
    },
